    color: "",
    description: "Elevate your terrace style with the adidas Campus 00s \"BAPE - World Cup Pack\" (KJ8851) in Black/White. Released as part of a high-profile collaboration for the 2026 World Cup, this pair reimagines the chunky, skate-inspired 00s silhouette with A Bathing Ape’s signature luxury flair.The upper is drenched in premium black patent leather featuring a deep croc-embossed texture, giving the classic low-top a high-fashion edge. This is sharply contrasted by crisp white serrated Three Stripes and a matching heel tab, while gold-foil \"CAMPUS\" and BAPE branding add a touch of championship-tier prestige. Small but impactful details-like the custom gold lace dubrae and the iconic Ape Head logo on the tongue-tie the look together. Anchored by a clean off-white midsole that maintains that authentic retro grip, this pair is a masterclass in blending streetwear royalty with heritage sports design.",
