    color: "",
    description: "It’s been all systems go for the Tennis Hu, the latest Pharrell Williams-branded shoe birthed from his collaborative relationship with adidas. The Three Stripes brand dropped this striking teal colorway summer ’17 as part of a four-shoe release that also included two multicolor options. The Stan Smith-inspired silhouette takes on a whole new life here, with a lightweight stretch-mesh upper dressed with yellow and tan accents. Dual branding appears on the tongues, heels and insoles. Speckled rope laces also add a nice touch. The outsole sports an interesting speckled design as well to complete the cozy kicks.",
