    collection: "Pharrell",
    price: 7974.00,
    currency: "ZAR",
    salePrice: 5911.10,
    category: ["men", "women", "sneakers"],
    sizes: ["36", "37", "37.5", "38", "38.5", "39", "39.5", "40", "40.5", "41", "41.5", "42", "42.5", "43", "43.5", "44", "44.5", "45", "46"],
    color: "",
    description: "The Pharrell x adidas PW 4D “Purple” is a hybrid model that fuses design elements from Pharrell’s Hu collection with the forward-thinking ethos of the 4D Futurecraft. The bold purple Primeknit-constructed upper provides a snug fit while remaining breathable and flexible. Painted white Three Stripes branding can be found on the mid-panel while the criss-crossed pattern of the four-dimensional midsole extends well into the heel and collar. The ribbed elastic collar features a Hu-branded patch. Mint-colored 4D soles provide tuned support and cushioning for unrivaled comfort. The Pharrell x adidas PW 4D “Purple” was released on December 20, 2019.",
    image: "shop/Sneakers/Adidas/adidas-shoes-pharrell/pw-4d-pharrell-williams-036531/pw-4d-pharrell-williams-fv6335/2ZQE5RmFazBbFy7wUCcoraM6.png",
